    "description": "Dodge obstacles, kill monsters, and collect coins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/ee0af3e31fb415b63f0b4f19f01fe851.poster.avif?t=1651319054\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/ee0af3e31fb415b63f0b4f19f01fe851.webm?t=1651319054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/ee0af3e31fb415b63f0b4f19f01fe851.mp4?t=1651319054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your coins wisely, you can level up, reset your status points, heal your HP or buy extra lives.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/640eab80825548dd78b374e663ec0d0a.poster.avif?t=1651319054\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/640eab80825548dd78b374e663ec0d0a.webm?t=1651319054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/640eab80825548dd78b374e663ec0d0a.mp4?t=1651319054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each level you up, you gain a status point. With these, you can choose which status you want to upgrade. There isn't a max level, by the way, you will level up how many times you can.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/86f7bce2eebfaf2123f2a76bd9ec48fa.poster.avif?t=1651319054\" width=200 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898570/extras/86f7bce2eebfaf2123f2a76bd9ec48